snippet.title: Syrian American Medical Society- SAMS
snippet.description: Welcome to SAMS official YouTube Channel! The Syrian American Medical Society (SAMS) is a global medical relief organization that is working on the front lines of crisis relief in Syria and beyond to save lives and alleviate suffering. SAMS proudly provides dignified medical care to every patient in need.
